# Trading Journal Updates Implementation Plan

This plan details the modifications requested for various sections of the trading journal, including Settings, Calendar, Operations, and the New Trade form.

## User Review Required
> [!IMPORTANT]
> The database schema will be updated to include a new field: `closeTime` (Orario chiusura trade) and a new setting field `isBarrierEnabled` (to toggle the barrier feature). This requires modifying `shared/schema.ts` and potentially creating a migration or directly altering the database using `script/alter_db_v2.ts`.

