## Verification Plan
### Automated Tests
- TypeScript compilation check (`npm ml -c "tsc --noEmit"` or similar) to verify schema changes don't break types.

### Manual Verification
- Start the dev server.
- Verify that a user can toggle weekend days in the calendar.
- Verify clicking a trade in the calendar opens its details.
- Verify duplicating a trade keeps the original trade's date.
- Verify selecting "Stop" auto-fills `-1%` (or negative value of risk) in the "Risultato" field, and "BE" auto-fills `0%`.
- Verify you can paste an image directly from the clipboard to attach it to the trade.
- Verify stats remain accurate visually.
